actionTypes.value:
Table: Output  
Field: The specific output of this code depends on the input recordId and the data in the Airtable base. However, the code always produces an output object via setOutputs(). The possible outputs are as follows:

- If the Streak Occurrence record is missing:
  - ok: false
  - actionOut: "skipped_missing_streak_occurrence"
  - statusOut: "skipped"
  - errorOut: "Streak Occurrence not found: {recordId}"

- If the Streak Occurrence is inactive:
  - ok: true
  - actionOut: "skipped_inactive_streak_occurrence"
  - statusOut: "skipped"
  - errorOut: ""
  - streakOccurrenceId: {recordId}

- If the Streak Occurrence Source Status is not "Ready for XP":
  - ok: true
  - actionOut: "skipped_not_ready_for_xp"
  - statusOut: "skipped"
  - errorOut: ""
  - streakOccurrenceId: {recordId}
  - sourceStatus: {sourceStatus}

- If already linked to an XP Event:
  - ok: true
  - actionOut: "skipped_already_linked_to_xp_event"
  - statusOut: "skipped"
  - errorOut: ""
  - streakOccurrenceId: {recordId}
  - linkedXpEventCount: {number}

- If required values are missing:
  - ok: false
  - actionOut: "error_missing_required_streak_values"
  - statusOut: "error"
  - errorOut: "Missing required value for XP creation."
  - streakOccurrenceId: {recordId}
  - enrollmentId: {enrollmentId}
  - achievementId: {achievementId}
  - streakEndDateKey: {streakEndDateKey}
  - streakDays: {streakDays}

- If Achievement is missing:
  - ok: false
  - actionOut: "error_missing_achievement"
  - statusOut: "error"
  - errorOut: "Achievement not found: {achievementId}"
  - streakOccurrenceId: {recordId}

- If no active XP Reward Rule is found:
  - ok: false
  - actionOut: "error_missing_xp_reward_rule"
  - statusOut: "error"
  - errorOut: "No active XP Reward Rule found. Tried: {allowedRuleKeys}"
  - streakOccurrenceId: {recordId}
  - achievementName: {achievementName}
  - allowedRuleKeys: {allowedRuleKeys}

- If XP Reward Rule has no positive XP Amount:
  - ok: false
  - actionOut: "error_invalid_xp_amount"
  - statusOut: "error"
  - errorOut: "XP Reward Rule has no positive XP Amount: {xpRuleId}"
  - streakOccurrenceId: {recordId}
  - achievementName: {achievementName}
  - xpRuleId: {xpRuleId}

- If XP Event is created or updated successfully:
  - ok: true
  - actionOut: "created_xp_event" or "updated_xp_event"
  - statusOut: "success"
  - errorOut: ""
  - streakOccurrenceId: {recordId}
  - xpEventId: {xpEventId}
  - enrollmentId: {enrollmentId}
  - achievementId: {achievementId}
  - achievementName: {achievementName}
  - streakDays: {streakDays}
  - streakEndDateKey: {streakEndDateKey}
  - weekId: {weekId or ""}
  - xpAmount: {xpAmount}
  - xpRuleId: {xpRuleId}
  - sourceKey: {sourceKey}
  - duplicateXpEventsMarkedInactive: {number}

The actual output will be one of these objects, depending on the data and the state of the input record.

Table: Submissions  
Field: Daily Email Subject  
Output: Daily Submission Received - {Athlete Name} - {Activity Date}

Field: Daily Email HTML  
Output: Branded HTML email summarizing the submission, including athlete name, activity date, week, submission stats, XP, homework submitted, homework assigned, grading status, weekly progress, and footer links.

Field: Daily Email To  
Output: CSV of deduplicated parent and athlete emails from Enrollment (Parent Email - Cleaned and Athlete Email - Cleaned).

Field: Daily Email Version  
Output: v2 (or value of input variable emailVersion if provided)

Field: Daily Email Status  
Output: Ready (single select)

Field: Daily Email Sent to Make.com Status  
Output: Ready (single select)

Field: Send Daily Email to Make Now?  
Output: true

Field: Build Daily Email Now?  
Output: false

Field: Daily Email Sent to Make.com At  
Output: null

Other outputs (via output.set):  
- statusOut: success  
- recordId: {recordId}  
- enrollmentId: {enrollmentId}  
- weekId: {weekId}  
- weeklySummaryId: {weeklySummaryId}  
- subjectOut: {subject}  
- htmlOut: {html}  
- dailyEmailTo: {recipientCsv}  
- recipientsCsv: {recipientCsv}  
- emailVersion: {emailVersion}  
- submissionXp: {submissionXpInfo.xp}  
- weeklyXp: {weeklyXpInfo.xp}  
- weekShots: {weekShots}  
- weekMakes: {weekMakes}  
- currentShootingStreak: {currentShootingStreak}  
- currentShootingStreakAsOf: {currentShootingStreakAsOf}  
- currentShootingStreakStatus: {currentShootingStreakStatus}  
- errorOut: "" (empty string if success, error message if error)

If an error occurs, Daily Email Status and Daily Email Sent to Make.com Status are set to Error, Build Daily Email Now? and Send Daily Email to Make Now? are set to false, and errorOut contains the error message.
